{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0026", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "framework", "content": "Effective AI prompts share a specific architecture comprising five layers: Identity, Context, Task, Process, and Output. This structure maps to how models process and prioritize information.", "line_start": 165, "line_end": 167, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.7, 0.4, 0.1, 0.3, 0.8, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0027", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "concept", "content": "The 'Identity' layer of a prompt defines the model's specific, fine-tuned role, skill expertise, and perspectives, going beyond generic labels like 'helpful assistant'.", "line_start": 170, "line_end": 172, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.6, 0.5, 0.1, 0.2, 0.7, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0028", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "claim", "content": "Assigning a specific identity to an AI model, such as 'senior product marketer specializing in B2B SaaS positioning,' causes it to access different clusters of training data, stylistic patterns, skill patterns, and reasoning approaches.", "line_start": 177, "line_end": 181, "chaperone": {"context_type": "consensus", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.5, 0.6, 0.1, 0.3, 0.6, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0029", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "concept", "content": "The 'Context' layer of a prompt provides the model with necessary background information, prior decisions, and constraints that would be obvious to a human but invisible to the AI.", "line_start": 185, "line_end": 187, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.5, 0.5, 0.1, 0.2, 0.7, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0030", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "praxis_hook", "content": "Context provided to an AI model must be ordered, scoped, and labeled to prevent the model from treating all information as equally optional, as it pattern-matches relevance rather than 'remembering' emotionally.", "line_start": 192, "line_end": 196, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.4, 0.6, 0.1, 0.2, 0.8, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0031", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "concept", "content": "The 'Task' layer of a prompt defines the specific action the AI must take, requiring precise definitions like 'produce a 500-word product description emphasizing time-saving benefits for busy executives' rather than vague requests.", "line_start": 200, "line_end": 202, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.5, 0.5, 0.1, 0.2, 0.8, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0032", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "concept", "content": "The 'Process' layer of a prompt instructs the model on how to approach a task, describing the thinking order, decision checkpoints, and internal validation steps, rather than just requesting an output.", "line_start": 207, "line_end": 217, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.7, 0.4, 0.1, 0.3, 0.9, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0033", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "praxis_hook", "content": "When prompting an AI, describe the desired process (e.g., 'First, analyze the target audience... Then, define the positioning... Then, write the page... Show your reasoning at each step. Do not skip steps, and audit your work following') rather than just asking for a direct output.", "line_start": 210, "line_end": 213, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "evidence", "tension_vector": [0.6, 0.5, 0.1, 0.2, 0.9, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
{"atom_id": "ATOM-SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you-0034", "source_id": "SOURCE-20260127-x-article-kloss_xyz-why_you_suck_at_prompting_and_the_system_to_fix_you", "category": "concept", "content": "The 'Output' layer of a prompt specifies what a completed task should look like, including format requirements (e.g., 'Output your response as a JSON with inputs for headline, subheadline, and body text. Do not return any messaging, chat, notes, etc. Only the JSON').", "line_start": 222, "line_end": 226, "chaperone": {"context_type": "method", "argument_role": "claim", "tension_vector": [0.5, 0.5, 0.1, 0.2, 0.8, 0.7], "opposes_atom_ids": []}, "extensions": {}}
